Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This strange story began\Non a blistering hot day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had received an unexpected mail\Nfrom an old acquaintance of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the message was just this:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Seek the sacred beast from Anzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am at the meeting place of the four gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao, the sender of the message,\Nwas an acquaintance of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it didn't mean that we\Nkept in touch all that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew suspicious, and started to\Nresearch Pao's current whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Pao is one of the three\Ngreatest Feng Shui masters here on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I found his whereabouts,\Nhe had already left this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you weren't\Nthe one that sent me this mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who visits from\Nthe inauspicious back door...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Receive the word from the heavens,\Nand lead me to the sun stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what the {\i1}pa-kua {\i0}told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you shooting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are disrespectful fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot!\N--Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi of Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over there... Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's a new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, she's rather young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird one, hot dog bun, loved one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's his secret love-child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, she's rather old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Child, mild, wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting Pao's\Ndaughter to be this old already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I met you once\Nwhen you were this little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just an acquaintance.\NIt's been 10 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your father sure was unlucky\Nto be in a traffic accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the way to Jupiter, there was a sudden\Nspatial fluctuation in hyperspace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the "girlfriend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the "secret love-child"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jet, why were you at the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody outside the family\Nknows he got into an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Seek the sacred beast from Anzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am at the meeting place of the four gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao sent me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right before the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Can you help me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is the\Nwhereabouts of the sun stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sun stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The direction, day, and time you arrived\Nwas the best combination for Feng Shui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when you're\Nsearching for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mr. Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. About that, we will have it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the boss feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it could be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any particular favors\Nto repay to Pao or this girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I decided to help them for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were too many things that\Nmade me suspicious to leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Pao send me mail\Nright before his death?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do those words mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were those guys that attacked us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was something about\Nthis girl named Meifa as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This universe is made of three different Chis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is the Chi of Heaven,\Nthe energy that comes from the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is the Chi of Earth, the energy\Nthat comes from a planet's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And lastly Chi of Magnetism, the Chi\Nthat organisms like ourselves produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi from organisms?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human body always\Nproduces a magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That magnetic field and the\Nmagnetic field of the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,react to one another to create energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Universal Feng Shui is the technology that\Nreads the energies of nature such as this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to use them in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Universal Feng Shui...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same thing as fortunetelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other fortunetelling methods\Nonly predict or prognosticate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Universal Feng Shui has the\Npower to make the bad into the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if you were a Feng Shui\Nmaster as powerful as my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized that I never spent\Ntime like this with my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me point out that I'm not that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I would be a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, that would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least I can be an elder\Nbrother or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ice {\i0}cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mr. Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that "Anzan" refers to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mountain Hotel Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seiryu{\i0}! [Blue Dragon]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Byakko{\i0}! [White Tiger]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Genbu{\i0}! [Black Turtle]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suzaku{\i0}! [Scarlet Phoenix]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, the cross-zenith method!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun stone is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are. They're right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bottle of {\i1}lao-chu{\i0}. I don't need a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, you think we would\Ntell you that easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're from the Blue Snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are {\i0}from a syndicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you following us around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I couldn't tell you that\Neven if you killed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was because we couldn't get Pao...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they told us to get\Nthe recipient of his mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the low end so we\Ndon't know any more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father... is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao's words showed where this stone was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Pao is\Nstill alive somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he want me to find this stone\Nand do something with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I created more\Nmysteries instead of solving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I decided to check out\Nthis stone, which was our only clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a piece of the moon from\Nthat Gate Accident 50 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Feng Shui masters call it the sun stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absorbed the fluctuations\Nin time and space
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and conceals a tremendous\Namount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only think of it as a plain old rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how much would it be if we sold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, if you're gonna smoke,\Ngo smoke outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always smoke in here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm turning this into a\Nnonsmoking area starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, you're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is {\i1}my {\i0}ship, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do with this stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what my father is thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}luo-pan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be... I took the magnet off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly,\Nmy father owned a sun stone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that the two\Nstones are resonating
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to show me the whereabouts of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why Pao made\Nyou look for this stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why my father\Nsent the mail to you, Mr. Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and not to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dangerous combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more righteous a guy was in his youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more likely he's gonna fall\Nfor a young girl later in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... Guys are so clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was one that believed in Universal\NFeng Shui, but not other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my mother left the house,\Nand took me along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure my father was able to\Nfind our whereabouts easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he never even tried to look for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there was a reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was my father targeted by those men?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it because he was\Nfriends with bad people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who my father really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao... was the consultant for a syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao had leaked information to me about\Nthe syndicate, back when I was a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao already wanted out of\Nthe syndicate back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's impossible\Nfor someone who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,important syndicate secrets\Nto ever leave the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Pao was afraid that more\Nbad things would happen to his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure you can confirm\Nit all when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No response.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be... I'm sure this is the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spike, Faye, please take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they {\i1}your {\i0}guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out if you don't\Nwanna die with this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What rotten luck of the draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it's good to act without\Nasking "What's in it for me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fairies who are going\Nto grant the princess' wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unmanned fighters...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these would be the seven dwarves...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! They're trying to scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spike! Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, if we apply\Nlots of energy to that stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can draw out all the\Nforces trapped inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an all-or-nothing plan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what it is, just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast this rock with your plasma cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a great plan this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made it in time, Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao! You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meifa... It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pao, you're in unstable territory.\NI can't approach any closer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... There isn't any\Noxygen left in here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent you that mail because I wanted\Nyou to bring my daughter here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... you willed us to be here\Nlike this using Feng Shui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Pao.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:21:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meifa is here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because she {\i1}wanted {\i0}to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I was being too hotheaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meifa... it's wondertul to\Nsee you one last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I despised you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I don't know if it was a good thing\Nor a bad thing that we took her along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this was how\Nthis strange case ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went back to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the smoking ban was\Nlifted from the living quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, unchanging daily life\Nhas returned, just as it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing that has changed, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer read the\Nfortunetelling pages in magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too much time has passed by...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to lament that we were deeply in love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind keeps blowing, while my heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...cannot heal all the tears in it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone, cry for me with parched eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The real folk blues.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only want to know what true sadness is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sitting in muddy water...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...isn't such a bad life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...if it ends after the first time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... came with a whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man, Andy, made a sudden\Nappearance on horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an ally or a foe?\NOr is he a true cowboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode is a shocking sci-fi\Nmacaroni-western epic saga: "Cowboy Funk."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.73,0:24:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't this world view a bit different?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.74,0:24:36.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cowboy Funk"
